xa-ʿafrī̀t| plíṭɛle gu-yàma,| hóle xá-sanduqa dwíqa hátxa rəš-rúše dìye.|
ʾə̀θyɛle,| ʾə́θyɛle l-d-ay-ʾilàna.|
